{"type":"message","id":"7d4f64a7","parentId":"095d2c61","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:47:07.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！你的两个机器人都提示 \"You are not authorized to use this command\"，这是因为 OpenClaw 的 Telegram 配置中启用了 `allowlist` 策略。\n\n从你的配置中可以看到：\n```json\n\"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\",\n\"groupPolicy\": \"allowlist\"\n```\n\n但是还有一个关键的 allowlist 文件需要配置。让我检查一下 allowFrom 配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4731fe1aecb442b1970051fc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/credentials/telegram-default-allowFrom.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":17341,"output":118,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772095621985}}
