{"type":"message","id":"6319538a","parentId":"2a50d2cf","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:00:11.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"啊！现在问题清楚了。这个错误信息说明 OpenClaw 的 Gateway 只绑定到了本地回环地址（loopback），而 Telegram 机器人需要能够从外网访问你的 OpenClaw 服务。\n\n从你的配置中可以看到：\n```json\n\"gateway\": {\n  \"port\": 18789,\n  \"mode\": \"local\",\n  \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n  ...\n}\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n你需要将 Gateway 绑定到 LAN 地址，或者配置一个公网 URL。\n\n**选项1：绑定到 LAN（如果你在局域网内使用）**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set gateway.bind lan\n```\n\n**选项2：配置公网 URL（推荐）**\n如果你有公网 IP 或域名，可以配置：\n```bash\nopenclaw config set plugins.entries.telegram.config.publicUrl https://your-domain.com:18789\n```\n\n**选项3：使用 Tailscale（如果已安装）**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set gateway.tailscale.mode on\n```\n\n**最简单的临时解决方案：**\n\n既然你是在服务器上运行 OpenClaw，我建议先设置绑定到 LAN：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eb88e40436e2458a8455bb15","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config set gateway.bind lan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":18831,"output":275,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772096398892}}
